SENTIMENT ANALYSIS ON HOTEL REVIEW:

Model: Logistic Regression

STEPS:

1. Import DataSet
2. EDA
3. Missing Value if Any!
4. Check Distribution of Review Type - Not Happy and Happy
5. Drop unwanted columns
6. Apply Text Cleaning - Level 1 and Level 2
7. Train Test Split
8. Create Instance for TF-IDF Vectorizer and Logistic Regression
9. Train Model
10. Do Prediction
11. Plot Confusion Matrix
12. Check Accuracy, Precision and Recall
13. Test on Dummy Text String.
